## 4. The Hand Feel Experience

- Impact Sensation
    - Hardness Words: Firm, crisp, direct, explosive.
    - Feedback: Very clear, sharp feedback upon ball impact.
    - Hold vs. Release: Immediate release. It shoots the ball out much faster than it holds it.
    - Dwell Time: Short. The thin topsheet combined with the high-tension sponge severely limits pocketing time.

- Sound/Click
    - Produces a loud, metallic ESN click when hitting deeply through the sponge, which is very satisfying on power shots.

